In preparing this thesis, I used several AI-assisted tools for research, writing, and
implementation support. I used Gemini for initial research and to identify relevant
background material and sources. I used Claude models by Anthropic through Cursor and
OpenAI models through Codex to discuss design alternatives, refine the structure and
wording of sections, and support implementation work. In addition, I used Grammarly
for grammar and style correction. I carefully reviewed all AI-assisted text and code
and take responsibility for the correctness and integrity of the final work.
